title: Warhammer 40k Dark Heresy 2E Collection August 2016
description:
Included in this forbidden collection are:

Dark Heresy 2E Core Rulebook (DH19)

Dark Heresy 2E Game Master's Kit Book (DH20)

Dark Heresy 2E Game Master's Kit Screen (DH20)

Dark Heresy 2E Forgotten Gods (DH22) - first published adventure for Dark Heresy 2E

Dark Heresy 2E Enemies Within (DH23) - additional character options for joining Ordo Hereticus

Dark Heresy 2E Enemies Without (DH24) - supplement to have characters join Ordo Xenos

Dark Heresy 2E Enemies Beyond (DH25) - supplement to have character join Ordo Malleus



All are original electronic format (OEF) PDFs.



The God Emperor Provides
